Author: etherealaqua
Text: from google:  relatively: in relation, comparison, or proportion to something else.  technically we’re all relatively thin then! try not to stress over it too much (though I would too) and maybe focus on the fact that compared to most others you ARE thin otherwise he wouldn’t have said so!! but unless you are very literally THE most underweight person on earth, we’ll always be “relatively” as opposed to “absolutely” thin. idk idk I hope this helps though!

Author: LowCalPal
Text: If I were to guess I’d think it means in the lower half of a healthy BMI range
